	quest.163044CFA43079A9.quest_desc: [
		"    The &#4C566AWitcher Techniques&r book has 4 different Witcher combat spells:"
		""
		"• &#4C566AWitcher Reflexes&r - briefly block attacks and projectiles."
		""
		"• &#4C566ABattle Trance&r - increases movement speed and physical damage by 10% per adrenaline level for 5 seconds."
		""
		"• &#4C566ARend&r - powerful strike, damage scales with adrenaline level."
		""
		"• &#4C566AWhirl&r - area attacks, damage scales with adrenaline level."
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"    &#4C566AWitcher Sign Manual&r has 5 different Witcher sign spells:"
		""
		"• &3Aard&r - knocks back targets dealing damage."
		""
		"• &4Igni&r - continuous damage igniting targets."
		""
		"• &2Axii&r - stuns target and applies vulnerability for 5 seconds."
		""
		"• &6Quen&r - removes all negative effects and applies damage absorption for 10 seconds."
		""
		"• &5Yrden&r - 5 block radius field that slows and damages targets."
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"    &#4C566AMaster Witcher Book&r can hold up to 7 spells from &#4C566AWitcher Sign Manual&r, &#4C566AWitcher Techniques&r and &#4C566AEnhanced Signs&r."
		""
		"    &#4C566AEnhanced Signs&r:"
		""
		"• &3Aard Sweep&r - knocks back targets dealing damage."
		""
		"• &4Igni Fire-stream&r - continuous damage igniting targets."
		""
		"• &2Axii Puppet&r - turns enemy into ally and increases their damage."
		""
		"• &6Quen Active-shield&r - removes all negative effects, applies damage absorption and heals 50% of damage taken."
		""
		"• &5Yrden Magic Trap&r - creates sign glyph that destroys projectiles, damages and slows targets."
	]
	quest.163044CFA43079A9.quest_subtitle: "Craft the Book"
