	quest.310F6C5DAFD455D2.quest_desc: [
		"    The &#74DFBFTome of Water&r has 5 different water spells:"
		""
		"• &#74DFBFWater Whip&r (Main Spell) - When attacking a target, drenches it in water."
		""
		"• &#74DFBFBubble Beam&r - Deals sustained magic damage to targets, creates a small circle nearby that protects allies."
		""
		"• &#74DFBFSpringwater&r - Restores health and cleanses negative effects, also deals magic damage to targets."
		""
		"• &#74DFBFHydro Beam&r - A high-pressure beam dealing sustained damage."
		""
		"• &#74DFBFExplosive Bubblws&r - Slow bouncy bubbles, dealing damage and healing allies in area on impact."
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"    The &#8B4513Tome of Earth&r has 5 different earth spells:"
		""
		"• &#8B4513Stone Spear&r (Main Spell) - Shoots stone projectiles that explode on impact, dealing magic damage and applying the &#8B4513Bleeding&r effect."
		""
		"• &#8B4513Stone Flesh&r - Increases armor and toughness at full health, but the next attack deals half damage."
		""
		"• &#8B4513Terra Circle&r - Summons two circles of stalagmites from the ground and applies &#8B4513Bleeding&r to targets."
		""
		"• &#8B4513Earthquake&r - Causes an earthquake, throwing nearby targets around and dealing magic damage."
		""
		"• &#8B4513Shattering Stones&r - Stone projectile, that creates more projectiles on impact, dealing damage and inflicting &#8B4513Bleeding&r."
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"    The &#77CCFFTome of Wind&r book has 5 different air spells:"
		""
		"• &#77CCFFAir Cutter&r (Main Spell) - When attacking a target, knocks it back."
		""
		"• &#77CCFFAeroblast&r - When attacking a target, launches it upward."
		""
		"• &#77CCFFUpdraft&r - Deals sustained air damage; damage increases when the target is in the air."
		""
		"• &#77CCFFTornado&r - Summons a tornado that lifts and pulls targets into it."
		""
		"• &#77CCFFAeroburst&r - Pressure Burst, knocking targets in a circle back and dealing damage."
	]
	quest.310F6C5DAFD455D2.quest_subtitle: "Craft the Tome"
