	quest.49C7B92298881150.quest_desc: [
		"    The &2Archery Manual&r has 5 different Archer spells:"
		""
		"• &2Power Shot&r - Increases arrow damage by 10% for 12 seconds, stacks up to 2 times."
		""
		"• &2Entangling Roots&r - Creates roots from the ground around, slowing targets for 8 seconds."
		""
		"• &2Barrage&r - Rapidly fires 3 arrows in a row."
		""
		"• &2Magic Arrow&r - Pierces through, damaging up to 3 targets."
		""
		"• &2Ranger's Focus&r - Slows you drastically for 12 seconds, increases your eanged damage and velocity and decreasing pull time, but creates a area impact on arrow impact."
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"    The &#FF681FWar Archery Instructions&r has 5 different Archer spells:"
		""
		"• &#FF681FSmoldering Arrow&r - The arrow explodes on impact and burns nearby targets."
		""
		"• &#FF681FDual Shot&r - Quickly fires 2 arrows."
		""
		"• &#FF681FPoint-Blank Shot&r - The closer the target, the farther it is knocked back."
		""
		"• &#FF681FPin Down&r - The target cannot move or jump for 4 seconds."
		""
		"• &#FF681FFan of Fire&r - Calls explosive arrows, in an area dealing damage and setting enemies on fire."
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"    The &#88C0D0Tundric Hunting&r book has 5 different Archer spells:"
		""
		"• &#88C0D0Frozen Shot&r - Freezes and slows targets."
		""
		"• &#88C0D0Arctic Volley&r - Fires 8 arctic arrows and freezes targets."
		""
		"• &#88C0D0Frozen Pact&r - Deals magic damage according to its freeze and reduces the target's attack."
		""
		"• &#88C0D0Enchanted Crystal Arrow&r - Stuns and freezes targets."
		""
		"• &#88C0D0Winters Grip&r - Spawns a winter totem, slowing enemies, freezing other enemies around on death."
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"    The &#222222Deadeye's List&r has 5 different Archer spells:"
		""
		"• &#222222Fast Shot&r - With each shot, increases draw speed."
		""
		"• &#222222Trick Shot&r - The arrow ricochets from target to target, dealing damage and applying &#222222Bleeding&r."
		""
