	quest.578B21BA4828ECDB.quest_desc: [
		"    The &4Tome of Fire&r has 5 different Fire spells:"
		""
		"• &4Pyroblast&r (Main Spell) - Launches an explosive fireball that explodes in a 2.5 block radius."
		""
		"• &4Fire Breath&r - Continuous magic damage, igniting targets."
		""
		"• &4Meteor&r - Calls down meteors on the target in a 6 block radius."
		""
		"• &4Wall of Flames&r - Creates a wall of fire for 8 seconds, continuously damaging targets inside it."
		""
		"• &4Flamerush&r - Rushes forward and leaves flame clouds on the trail. Increasing movement speed and fire spell power."
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"    The &5Tome of Arcane&r has 5 different Arcane spells:"
		""
		"• &5Arcane Blast&r (Main Spell) - When attacking a target, applies the &5Mystic Charge&r effect, stacking up to 3 times."
		""
		"• &5Arcane Missiles&r - Shoots mystic arrows that pierce through 2 targets, dealing magic damage; with the &5Mystic Charge&r effect, damage increases."
		""
		"• &5Arcane Beam&r - A mystic beam dealing continuous magic damage; with the &5Mystic Charge&r effect, damage increases."
		""
		"• &5Blink&r - Teleports 15 blocks."
		""
		"• &5Falling Star&r - Calls a falling astral star, causing arcane spell damage. Consumes all Arcane Charges."
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"    The &bTome of Frost&r has 5 different Frost spells:"
		""
		"• &bFrostbolt&r (Main Spell) - Launches a frost orb that bounces and slows targets."
		""
		"• &bFrost Nova&r - Freezes nearby targets for 6 seconds, applies vulnerability to frost spells."
		""
		"• &bFrost Shield&r - Applies protection from attacks, projectiles, and fire for 8 seconds, but reduces movement speed."
		""
		"• &bBlizzard&r - Calls down a rain of frost shards on targets and slows them in a 3 block radius."
		""
		"• &bRay of Frost&r - Casts a cold beam, causing frost spell damage and slowing the target."
	]
	quest.578B21BA4828ECDB.quest_subtitle: "Craft the Tome"
