	quest.6660E7EC61427D59.quest_desc: [
		"• &#B48EADDischarge III&r - Increases &#B48EADspeed&r when attacking, but at high speeds &#B48EADreleases accumulated energy&r as an explosion dealing damage to all. Can only be applied to a Sword."
		""
		"• &#B48EADEnsnaring IV&r - Chance to &#B48EADslow&r the target, also releases &#B48EADfangs around&r dealing damage to targets. Can only be applied to a Sword."
		""
		"• &#B48EADCurse of Lolth&r (Curse) - Chance to &#B48EADrestore health&r, but may spawn &#B48EADspiders from your body&r, which take increased damage. Can only be applied to a Sword."
		""
		"• &#B48EADPurification III&r - Chance to neutralize negative effects of &#B48EADwither&r and &#B48EADpoison&r, releasing accumulated energy as an &#B48EADexplosion&r dealing damage to targets. Can only be applied to Armor."
		""
		"• &#B48EADVoltaic Shot&r - Charges &#B48EADarrows with energy&r, allowing arrows to fly &#B48EADwithout ballistics&r in a straight line, dealing explosive damage. Can only be applied to a Crossbow."
	]
